<span class="header1">Arts/Communications paired with Public Service (BG)</span>

<p>If you scored high in the "B" and "G" categories, you are a very independent person. Your "no-nonsense" approach ensures that things get done. You are creative, responsible, and outgoing. You enjoy working with others, but can work alone. More than likely, you will choose an occupation that will help your community.</p>
<p>Most occupations in this pairing require at least a Bachelor's Degree. In certain occupations, it is valuable to have a Master's Degree or a Ph.D.</p>

